VALUES
	(1,2,'2012-11-24 00:33:40','2012-11-24 00:33:40','After 8 years of living in sin, we&#039;re making it official! Thanks for all the love.\r\n\r\nHope you can join us for a \"M&#039;Lord and M&#039;Lady&#039;s Royal Engagement Party\" at the Stash Bar (14th St and 8th Ave) on Saturday, January 12 at 9:00 PM. <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/events/388556324551822/\">RSVP here</a>.','Finally!','','publish','closed','closed','','hello-world','','','2013-04-19 22:04:46','2013-04-19 22:04:46','',0,'http://scottyandallie.com/?p=1',0,'post','',0),
	(2,2,'2012-11-24 00:33:40','2012-11-24 00:33:40','[caption id=\"attachment_124\" align=\"alignleft\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/198175_553009123173_4336_n.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-124\" src=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/198175_553009123173_4336_n-300x224.jpg\" alt=\"One of many nights spent at Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse in Tallahassee\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" /></a> One of many nights spent at Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse in Tallahassee in 2004[/caption] \r\n\r\nAllie and Scott met on the evening of September 19, 2004 at Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse in Tallahassee, Florida.  She was a grad student studying politics and he was musician/facemelter.\r\n\r\nOn that fateful evening, Allie and her friend, Sally Harris, decided to go to Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse for Sunday night drink specials and free Gumby\'s pizza. Scott and his bandmate, Andrew Altman, had the same idea.\r\n\r\nAllie and Sally invited the boys to join them for Jaeger shots. Because our families will be reading this, we\'re going to leave it at that.\r\n\r\nTheir first date was going to a Michael Moore rally the night before the 2004 election.\r\n\r\nFast forward two years later, Allie had moved to Manhattan and Scotty was living in Nashville while touring. Scott\'s tour finally ended with a show in NYC and he hasn\'t left the city since.\r\n\r\nFast forward six years later: Allie had just finished cleaning Lulu\'s litter box and was about to leave the apartment to go to Jersey for Thanksgiving with Scott. Scott then said \"I have something to give you.\" He pulled out a box and Allie said \"is this for me?\"\r\n\r\n[caption id=\"attachment_166\" align=\"alignright\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/10314665_10104482274273273_2468717422954754602_n.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-166\" src=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/10314665_10104482274273273_2468717422954754602_n-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"9.5 years later, after losing a bunch of weight last year!\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" /></a> 9.5 years later, after losing a bunch of weight last year![/caption]\r\n\r\nExactly 23 minutes later Allie had already purchased a copy of \"Brides\" magazine. Our wedding will be a celebration of TEN years together. And no, we will NOT be arriving in a horse drawn carriage.','How We Met','','publish','closed','closed','','how-we-met','','','2015-01-29 09:35:19','2015-01-29 09:35:19','',0,'http://scottyandallie.com/?page_id=2',1,'page','',3),
