	(9,2,'2013-10-21 04:33:32','2013-10-21 04:33:32','Allie and Scott met on the evening of September 19, 2004 at Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse in Tallahassee, Florida.  She was a grad student studying politics and he was musician/facemelter/taco sampler.\n\nOn that fateful evening, Allie and her friend, Sally Harris, decided to go to Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse for Sunday night drink specials and free Gumby\'s pizza. Scott and his bandmate, Andrew Altman, had the same idea.\n\nAllie and Sally invited the boys to join them for Jaeger shots. Because our families will be reading this, we\'re going to leave it at that.\n\nTheir first date was going to a Michael Moore rally the night before the 2004 election.\n\nFast forward two years later, Allie had moved to Manhattan and Scotty was living in Nashville while touring. Scott\'s tour finally ended with a show in NYC and he hasn\'t left the city since.\n\nFast forward six years later: Allie had just finished cleaning Lulu\'s litter box and was about to leave the apartment to go to Jersey for Thanksgiving with Scott. Scott then said \"I have something to give you.\" He pulled out a box and Allie said \"is this for me?\"\n\nExactly 23 minutes later Allie had already purchased a copy of \"Brides\" magazine. Stay tuned for a wedding probably featuring rockstar karaoke, Southern BBQ and a Chuppah. And no, we will NOT be arriving in a horse drawn carriage.\n\n[caption id=\"attachment_124\" align=\"alignnone\" width=\"300\"]<a href=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/198175_553009123173_4336_n.jpg\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-124\" alt=\"One of many nights spent at Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse in Tallahassee\" src=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/198175_553009123173_4336_n-300x224.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"224\" /></a> One of many nights spent at Poor Paul\'s Pourhouse in Tallahassee in 2004[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;','How We Met','','inherit','open','open','','2-autosave','','','2013-10-21 04:33:32','2013-10-21 04:33:32','',2,'http://scottyandallie.com/?p=9',0,'revision','',0),
	(192,3,'2015-01-29 08:54:35','2015-01-29 08:54:35','Our wedding will take place at <strong><a href=\"http://fullmooncentral.com\">Full Moon Resort</a></strong> in the the “Forever Wild” Catskill Forest Preserve in upstate New York. Dedicated to the celebration of nature, music and the arts, this one hundred-acre wonderland of mountains, fields, and streams is a world of its own. Full Moon is located in the mountains of the Hudson Valley, 30 minutes west of Woodstock, 2.5 hours from NYC.\n\nValley View Road\nBig Indian, NY 12410\nTel: (845) 254-5117\nwww.fullmoonresort.com\n\nClick to explore a map of the grounds.\n\n<a href=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/full-moon.png\"><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-228\" src=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/full-moon.png\" alt=\"full-moon\" width=\"600\" height=\"884\" /></a>','Full Moon Resort','','inherit','open','open','','117-autosave-v1','','','2015-01-29 08:54:35','2015-01-29 08:54:35','',117,'http://scottyandallie.com/2014/08/07/117-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(10,2,'2013-01-07 06:36:01','2013-01-07 06:36:01','After 8.2 years of living in sin, we\'re making it official! Thanks for all the love.\n\nHope you can join us for a \"M\'Lord and M\'Lady\'s Royal Engagement Party\" at the Ding Dong Lounge on Saturday, January 12. RSVP here.','Finally!','','inherit','open','open','','1-autosave','','','2013-01-07 06:36:01','2013-01-07 06:36:01','',1,'http://scottyandallie.com/?p=10',0,'revision','',0),
