	(202,3,'2014-09-01 15:14:35','2014-09-01 15:14:35','Erie and Allie hail from the neighboring New Jersey hamlets of Westfield and Mountainside. They met at the intersection of some mutual friends and Cosimo\'s, one of Allie\'s favorite hometown haunts. Ok let\'s be real -- they met while hammered at an Allman Brother\'s concert at PNC.','Erie McDonnell','','publish','closed','closed','','erie-mcdonnell','','','2014-09-21 23:21:55','2014-09-21 23:21:55','',0,'http://scottyandallie.com/?post_type=wedding_party&#038;p=202',0,'wedding_party','',0),
	(117,2,'2013-07-15 00:55:48','2013-07-15 00:55:48','Our wedding will take place at <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><a href=\"http://fullmooncentral.com\">Full Moon Resort</a></strong></span> in the the “Forever Wild” Catskill Forest Preserve in upstate New York. Dedicated to the celebration of nature, music and the arts, this one hundred-acre wonderland of mountains, fields, and streams is a world of its own. Full Moon is located in the mountains of the Hudson Valley, 30 minutes west of Woodstock, 2.5 hours from NYC.\r\n\r\nClick the map to explore the grounds.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/Map_FullMoon_2014.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-228 size-full\" src=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/full-moon.png\" alt=\"full-moon\" width=\"600\" height=\"884\" /></a>\r\n\r\n12 Valley View Road\r\nBig Indian, NY 12410\r\nTel: (845) 254-5117\r\nwww.fullmoonresort.com','Full Moon Resort','','publish','closed','closed','','full-moon-resort','','','2015-02-05 23:49:59','2015-02-05 23:49:59','',0,'http://scottyandallie.com/?page_id=117',3,'page','',0),
	(193,3,'2014-08-07 03:18:39','2014-08-07 03:18:39','<p class=\"p1\"><strong>FRIDAY</strong></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\">3pm — Guest checkin and snacks at Valley View House, lawn games, swimming, hanging.</p>\r\n7pm — Welcome BBQ in the Barn/Toasts and Roasts (Attire: Country chic/cocktail casual - sundress, Hawaiian shirts, etc)\r\n9pm —  Live Yacht Rock in the Barn with AMGold\r\n9pm — Campfire all night\r\n1am — Afterparty in the Billiards Room\r\n\r\n<strong>SATURDAY</strong>\r\n8:30–10:30am — Allie\'s Hangover Breakfast in the Cafe\r\n12:30pm-2pm — Scotty\'s Taco Bar Lunch in the Barn\r\n2pm — Kickball Game and Wiffle Ball Game in the Middle Field\r\n5pm — We get married in the Lower Grove! (Attire: Formal)\r\n6:00pm — Cocktail Hour on the Front Lawn\r\n7:00-11:00pm — PARTY! In the Reception Tent with Eturnity Band\r\n11:00pm - Sparkler parade to the After Party Jam at the Performance Space Bar With DJ Milky Manchester - bring your musical instruments or talents\r\n2:00am — After-After Party in the Billiards Room\r\n\r\nSunday\r\n8:30am-10:30am — Farewell brunch in the Cafe\r\n11am — Checkout\r\n\r\nThe pool is open daily from dawn to dusk.','Itinerary','','publish','closed','closed','','itinerary','','','2015-05-30 23:02:38','2015-05-30 23:02:38','',0,'http://scottyandallie.com/?page_id=193',0,'page','',0),
