	(188,3,'2014-06-03 03:31:59','2014-06-03 03:31:59','<a href=\"http://fullmooncentral.com/\"><img class=\"size-medium wp-image-121 aligncenter\" alt=\"indx_logo2bed1210\" src=\"http://scottyandallie.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/05/indx_logo2bed1210-300x146.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"146\" /></a>\n\nWe are SO EXCITED. Our wedding weekend will be Friday, June 5th through  Sunday, June 7th of 2015. \n\nThe location is <a href=\"http://www.fullmoonresort.com/\">Full Moon Resort</a> in Big Indian, NY.\n\nIt\'s going to be an awesome three day festival of family, friends, music, nature and love. Full Moon Resort is 20 minutes from Woodstock. It\'s on the top of a mountain so there\'s no cell phone service.\n\nMore details coming. Save the date!\n\n-Allie &amp; Scott','We have a date and a venue!','','inherit','open','open','','107-autosave-v1','','','2014-06-03 03:31:59','2014-06-03 03:31:59','',107,'http://scottyandallie.com/2014/06/03/107-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(207,2,'2015-05-29 12:12:45','2015-05-29 12:12:45','<p class=\"p1\"><strong>FRIDAY</strong></p>\n3pm — Guest checkin and snacks at Valley View House, lawn games, swimming, hanging.\n7pm — Welcome BBQ in the Barn/Toasts and Roasts (Attire: Country chic/cocktail casual - sundress, Hawaiian shirts, etc)\n9pm —  Live Yacht Rock in the Barn with AMGold\n9pm — Campfire all night\n1am — Afterparty in the Billiards Room\n\n<strong>SATURDAY</strong>\n8:30–10:30am — Allie\'s Hangover Breakfast in the Cafe\n12:30pm-2pm — Scotty\'s Taco Bar Lunch in the Barn\n2pm — Kickball Game and Wiffle Ball Game in the Middle Field\n5pm — We get married in the Lower Grove! (Attire: Formal, black tie optional.)\n6:00pm — Cocktail Hour on the Front Lawn\n7:00-11:00pm — PARTY! In the Reception Tent with Eturnity Band\n11:00pm - Sparkler parade to the After Party Jam at the Performance Space Bar With DJ Milky Manchester - bring your musical instruments or talents\n2:00am — After-After Party in the Billiards Room\n\nSunday\n8:30am-10:30am — Farewell brunch in the Cafe\n11am — Checkout\n\nThe pool is open daily from dawn to dusk.','Itinerary','','inherit','open','closed','','193-autosave-v1','','','2015-05-29 12:12:45','2015-05-29 12:12:45','',193,'http://scottyandallie.com/2014/09/21/193-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
